Singer Polina Gagarina Called Helping Weight Loss Products
Russian singer Polina Gagarina has named five products that helped her adjust the figure and subsequently not gain weight again.
The first on the list was water.
The singer prefers to drink clean non-carbonated water before each meal to dampen the feeling of hunger and eat less.
Also, vegetable salad, brown rice and seafood are ideal for maintaining slenderness.
Thanks to them, you can make a balanced diet: vegetables contain fiber, rice has complex carbohydrates, and seafood is a source of protein, beneficial vitamins and amino acids.
For the unloading days, the singer chooses apples.
Thanks to these products, Gagarina was able to get rid of 30 extra kilograms.
In addition, the singer switched to a fractional diet - eat often and a little and excluded from the diet fat, sweet and calorie.
Gagarina does not eat fried food, pastries, sausages and other meat semi-finished products, writes kp.ru July 26.
It also replaced red meat with fish and seafood.
Prefers vegetables (except potatoes), whole grains and lots of greens.
Also, Gagarina is actively engaged in the gym, yoga and running.
